<P>A Funeral-SERMON, Occa&s;ioned by the DEATH of Mrs. Sarah Leveret, (Once the Honourable CONSORT of JOHN LEVERET E&s;q. GOVERNOUR of the <HI>Ma&s;&s;achu|&s;et-Colony,</HI> NEW-ENGLAND,) Who changed Earth for Heaven. <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 letter"><HI>d.</HI> 11<HI>m.</HI> 1704.</P>
<P><HI>With an</HI> ELEGY <HI>upon her Memory.</HI></P>
